  description: 'In 1943, the U.S. Navy allegedly rendered a destroyer escort invisible and teleported it two hundred miles — with catastrophic consequences for the crew. The story of the Philadelphia Experiment has captivated conspiracy theorists for decades. But it all traces back to a single man: a troubled merchant mariner with a wild imagination and a taste for the dramatic. This is the true story behind one of the most enduring military legends of the twentieth century.',
